OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a fine
OL,6,Fand sunny evening, a dry night will
OL,7,Ffollow with clear spells and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Feeling warm and muggy,
OL,9,Fespecially in urban areas, bringing
OL,10,Fdifficult sleeping conditions.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMostly dry and bright on
OL,13,FMonday with sunny spells for all. The
OL,14,Fodd light shower is possible in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Feeling hot and humid.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,18,FRemaining dry and sunny throughout the
OL,19,Fperiod. Feeling hot by day in the
OL,20,Fstrong sunshine and increasingly warm
OL,21,Fand humid overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
